tool_description: This API returns links to different articles related to Women's health and Birth Control. This API was developed during the Make Space Hackathon 2.0.
name: Women Health and Birth Control
title: Women Health and Birth Control

api_list.name: Birth Control Related Content
api_list.description: This end-point pull birth control related content.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://women-health-and-birth-control.p.rapidapi.com/birth"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "women-health-and-birth-control.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
